330
00:18:45,708 --> 00:18:48,125
Aren't you too excited?

331
00:18:48,125 --> 00:18:50,875
Are you fooling around with me?

332
00:18:50,875 --> 00:18:52,875
No.

333
00:18:52,875 --> 00:18:56,792
It's my first time camping.

334
00:18:57,667 --> 00:19:00,958
So it's something new.

335
00:19:00,958 --> 00:19:06,958
To speak like an adventurer...
I'm... a little excited.

336
00:19:08,083 --> 00:19:09,750
What about you, Mr. Alvin?

337
00:19:11,042 --> 00:19:14,250
I've camped a few times before.

338
00:19:14,250 --> 00:19:16,000
But…

339
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:18,625
It's my first time camping

340
00:19:18,625 --> 00:19:20,917
with a companion.

341
00:19:20,917 --> 00:19:23,333
Mr. Alvin…

342
00:19:23,333 --> 00:19:25,083
You don't have friends, do you?

343
00:19:25,083 --> 00:19:26,958
You don't either.

344
00:19:28,167 --> 00:19:30,583
Phew, I'm going to sleep.

345
00:19:30,583 --> 00:19:33,333
It's so early. Are you an old man?

346
00:19:33,333 --> 00:19:36,750
I feel tired just by talking.

347
00:19:38,208 --> 00:19:39,958
You still seem energetic.

348
00:19:39,958 --> 00:19:41,417
Then I'll sleep first.

349
00:19:41,417 --> 00:19:43,375
It's fine.

350
00:19:43,375 --> 00:19:46,750
You must be physically and mentally exhausted
since you fell into the trap.

351
00:19:46,750 --> 00:19:49,750
Physical and mental fatigue
is 100% caused by you.

352
00:19:51,333 --> 00:19:54,458
Wake me up in three hours.

353
00:19:54,458 --> 00:19:57,625
Okay. In the meantime, I'll…

354
00:19:57,625 --> 00:19:59,083
All right. Please be alert.

355
00:19:59,083 --> 00:20:00,792
I'll sing a song.

356
00:20:00,792 --> 00:20:02,042
Why?

357
00:20:03,083 --> 00:20:05,083
